title: Balthazar Pierret
text: Balthazar Pierret (born 15 May 2000) is a French professional <a href="Association%20football">footballer</a> who plays as a <a href="Midfielder">central midfielder</a> for <a href="FC%20Dinamo%20Bucure%C8%99ti">Dinamo București</a>.<ref name="prosport/"><a href="https%3A//www.prosport.ro/fotbal-intern/liga-1/florin-raducioiu-transfer-ireal-la-dinamo-rezerva-liga-a-3-a-din-franta-19394650">Florin Răducioiu, transfer ireal la Dinamo: a adus un fotbalist care era rezervă în liga a 3-a din Franța!</a></ref>
